<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Thanks for giving PodRead a spin</h1>

    <p>Your premium plan has ended and you're on the free plan now.</p>

    <p>Your existing episodes and podcasts aren't going anywhere — they're yours. The free plan just has a shorter character limit and fewer voices.</p>

    <p>Credit packs are available in <a href="<%= @settings_url %>">Settings</a> if you want to keep creating episodes. Credits never expire.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
